itemLabel: Lt. Col. the Rt. Hon. Sir Gilbert Wills, 1st Baron Dulverton, Bt, MP, JP, OBE, ADC

wikipedia_page.main: Gilbert Alan Hamilton Wills, 1st Baron Dulverton (28 March 1880 – 1 December 1956), also known same Sir Gilbert Wills, 2nd Baronet of Northmoor & Manor Heath, was a British businessman and Conservative Member of Parliament from 1909-29.
